name: excess-processing-program-search-tool-c26e4
notes: This database is used to track and manage excess material from the three Divisions of Operation: Atlantic, Pacific, and Gulf.  In addition to supporting each division, the system also supports the Maritime Administration managers and engineers working with excess material.  EPP enables the Maritime Administration personnel to:- Record and manage excess material- Report on cost associated with excess material- Submit excess material data and images to General Services Administration's (GSA) GSAXcess web application in real-time- Manage the disposal of excess material via a streamlined, accurate and visible process
